config is GNOME Classic set in login mode

"Add to Favorites"

```
get the full list

```
ls /usr/share/applications/
```

then update

```
gsettings set org.gnome.shell favorite-apps "['firefox-esr.desktop', 'org.gnome.Terminal.desktop', 'org.gnome.gedit.desktop', 'org.gnome.Terminal.desktop', 'transmission-gtk.desktop', 'sublime_text.desktop', 'org.gnome.Nautilus.desktop']"
```


